skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: make me laugh
des: Ask Alexa to tell you corny Dad jokes when you need a laugh. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next joke. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
